# quarkus-fx

[![Version](https://img.shields.io/maven-central/v/io.quarkiverse.fx/quarkus-fx-parent?logo=apache-maven&style=flat-square)](https://search.maven.org/artifact/io.quarkiverse.fx/quarkus-fx)

